 📍 Le Node \, AQUINUM C/O Le Node - 12 rue des Faussets - 33000 Bordeaux
 \, Bordeaux \, France\n\nBonjour\,\nLe prochain club de lecture se tiendra
  au Node le samedi 02/12/2018 de 9h30 à 11h30.Le livre sélectionné est 
 “Start With Why” de Simon SINEK.\n“START WITH WHY shows that the lea
 ders who've had the greatest influence in the world all think\, act\, and 
 communicate the same way - and it's the opposite of what everyone else doe
 s. Sinek calls this powerful idea The Golden Circle\, and it provides a fr
 amework upon which organizations can be built\, movements can be led\, and
  people can be inspired. And it all starts with WHY.”\nBonne lecture\n\n
 Communauté: agile-bordeaux\n👥 14 participant(s)
