BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Club de lecture de novembre
DTSTART;TZID=Europe/Paris:20171108T190000
DTEND;TZID=Europe/Paris:20171108T210000
UID:https://www.meetup.com/agile-bordeaux/events/244046292/@community-even
 ts
DESCRIPTION:🔗 https://www.meetup.com/agile-bordeaux/events/244046292/\n
 📍 Le New York\, 4 Cours Pasteur\, Bordeaux\, France\n\nLe prochain club
  de lecture aura lieu mercredi 8 novembre à 19h00 au New York.\nLe livre 
 retenu est "Humans vs Computers" de Gojko Adzic.\nHumans vs Computers is
  a book about people caught between wrong assumptions and computer bugs. Y
 ou'll read about humans who are invisible to computers\, how a default p
 assword once caused a zombie apocalypse and why airlines sometimes give aw
 ay free tickets. This is also a book on how to prevent\, avoid and reduce 
 the impact of such problems.\nBonne lecture !\n\nCommunauté: agile-bordea
 ux\n👥 3 participant(s)
LOCATION:Le New York\, 4 Cours Pasteur\, Bordeaux\, France
TZID:Europe/Paris
URL:https://www.meetup.com/agile-bordeaux/events/244046292/
END:VEVENT
